{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217925, "create_time": 1655227579, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "左边比右边多了一个乒乓球的重量？", "timestamp": 1655227579}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217966, "create_time": 1655228419, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 右边比左边多了一个密度等于水体积等于乒乓球的重量", "timestamp": 1655228419}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217967, "create_time": 1655228426, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "排水量一样所以一样重？", "timestamp": 1655228426}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217977, "create_time": 1655228589, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "左边多个乒乓球的重量，右边多和铁球同体积水的重量", "timestamp": 1655228589}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217980, "create_time": 1655228614, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "比较：等体积的水 和 乒乓球 重量，水更重，选B\n", "timestamp": 1655228614}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217992, "create_time": 1655228979, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "这种题为什么会在你清的树洞引起讨论并且1/3的人做错...no offense...", "timestamp": 1655228979}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218048, "create_time": 1655231404, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Alice: 说明 Alice 是文科生", "timestamp": 1655231404}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218053, "create_time": 1655231640, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "来回炉初中\n，被子重量一样，消了\n水体积一样，消了\n那么要比：乒乓球的重量和铁球所受的浮力哪个大，根据阿基米德原理，乒乓球和铁球排开水的（体积）重量相同，而根据图示，乒乓球的重量小于浮力，所以铁球所受浮力大于乒乓球的重量，右侧更重。", "timestamp": 1655231640}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218057, "create_time": 1655232110, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "为啥两边水体积一样，难道不是放进去球之后的高度一样吗？所以左边多了一个乒乓球的重量", "timestamp": 1655232110}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218067, "create_time": 1655233430, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "分析杯子受力，杯子上面只和水和绳子（左边才有）接触，就只受水的压力和绳子的拉力。水的压力是一样的，左边还受一个绳子向上提的力。杯子受力平衡所以左边杯子的支持力小一些。两边之差就是乒乓球绳子的拉力，等于乒乓球浮力减去乒乓球重力。", "timestamp": 1655233430}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218072, "create_time": 1655233532, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "就是说管他什么球，你就隔离杯子作为研究对象，看对杯子的施力物体是啥，说白了就是初中知识。", "timestamp": 1655233532}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 230799, "create_time": 1655538137, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "整体来看左边就是水和杯子。右边也是水和杯子，消了。此外还有绳子的拉力（对铁球分析肯定浮力小于重力，所以绳子有拉力）。别的什么都不用考虑吧？不影响整体法吧？所以左边沉。", "timestamp": 1655538137}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 230803, "create_time": 1655538195, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re Jason: 你不考虑铁球和乒乓球质量吗？", "timestamp": 1655538195}], "create_time": 1655227330, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655538195, "likenum": 14, "n_attentions": 14, "n_comments": 13, "pid": 65500, "poll": {"answers": [{"option": "左", "votes": 21}, {"option": "右", "votes": 40}, {"option": "一样重", "votes": 17}, {"option": "🍉", "votes": 14}], "vote": null}, "reply": 13, "text": "\n![](https://gateway.ipfs.io/ipfs/bafkreidiqi6xtpv6ptslhrcscc4nw37cganbxdh7ih4hnhsf2x